{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b3d1689b7c","title":"中央转发邮电部党组关于三反报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"57229750c4","index":0,"year":1951,"month":12,"day":11,"articleId":"b3d1689b7c"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""},{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"92c32f6506","type":"title","text":"中央转发邮电部党组关于三反报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b3d1689b7c"},{"id":"0483636cb9","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b3d1689b7c"},{"id":"0e19a0a398","type":"appellation","text":"中央和军委各部门，中央人民政府各党组，各中央局，并请转发分局，省市区党委，地委和县委：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b3d1689b7c"},{"id":"b1cdb93ffa","type":"paragraph","text":"兹将中央邮电部党组关于反贪污反浪费反官僚主义报告一件发给你们。因邮电事业普及全国，贪污问题又很严重，故应将此件转发县委，提起大家注意。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b3d1689b7c"},{"id":"f1a1892179","type":"paragraph","text":" 中央十二月十一日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b3d1689b7c"}],"page":{"id":"b829d4dacd","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b3d1689b7c","start":0,"end":0}},"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"152fc15ce2","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"b3d1689b7c","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"邮电部党组1951年12月7日的三反报告指出，邮电系统的贪污案件，除一般旧社会常有的类型外，尚有与专门业务相结合的专业贪污案，且极为普遍。贪污腐化现象滋长的原因，一是全国解放以后，反贪污反浪费尚未形成广泛深入的群众运动，加之党内生活、政治教育不健全，资本主义反过来引诱与腐蚀我们：二是县邮电局多原封未动，领导方面忽视了县局的改造与加强；三是对惩治贪污犯采取了姑息态度，片面地理解“不能轻易开除人”与“不能造成工人的失业”，客观上助长了资污化的风气。"}],"contents":[{"id":"152fc15ce2","type":"paragraph","text":"中央和军委各部门，中央人民政府各党组，客中央局，并请转发分局，省市区党委，地委和县委：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"b3d1689b7c"},{"id":"1d5c400130","type":"subtitle","text":"中央","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"b3d1689b7c"},{"id":"1f4efefb8d","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月十一日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"b3d1689b7c"},{"id":"2f4b78256b","type":"title","text":"中央转发邮电部党组关于三反报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"b3d1689b7c"},{"id":"c4d32d57a7","type":"paragraph","text":"兹将中央邮电部党组关于反贪污反浪费反官主义报告一件发给你们。因邮电事业普及全国，贪污问题又很严重，故应将此件转发县委，提起大家注意。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"b3d1689b7c"}],"page":{"id":"6143c4d941","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"b3d1689b7c","start":123,"end":123}}}},"__N_SSG":true}